details.name: Prince Tybalt
details.text: Whew, the think I can take a short break... Grim is really determined to get me. I hope that my father is well.

details.name: Prince Tybalt
details.text: Thankfully, my call for help I sent to Jade Twilight went through, and they sent some forces to cover my back.

details.name: Prince Tybalt
details.text: There is another camp not far from here. I can take some proper rest there. I wonder if they brought some of their tropical drinks with them.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Well, well well. If it isn't the cowardly Prince, still on the run.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: And Jade Twilight! I did not expect they would come to his aid. This complicates matters.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Luckily, the reinforcements I ordered from President Gideon are here.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: This is Warlord Grim, sending urgent request to General Cyrus. Jade Twilight has joined the Ruby Dusk in their assault on our kingdom. Please assist in clearing their base.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Jade Twilight attacking? Are you sure? They are a peaceful nation. If they are here, it must be for a good reason. Let me talk to their commanding officer.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: He's not buying it. I have to tell Gideon to send someone more compliant next time. Plan B it is.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Knights, begin your attack on Jade installations.

details.name: Knight Infantry
details.text: As you wish, Warlord.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Our forces are engaged in combat with Jade Twilight invaders. Please assist!

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: This is madness. But we still have our orders.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: General Cyrus to Amber Noon forces, we are coming.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: There is a temporary Airfield on our flank. I'm sure they are planning to hit us from the side with their air forces. Take it out before going ahead.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Copy that.
Capture the Jade Twilight buildings.
General Cyrus must survive.
(Optional) Capture the Jade Twilight Airfield.

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: I have made a tactical mistake! Fall back!

details.name: Prince Tybalt
details.text: General! I beg you to stop!

details.name: General Cyrus
details.text: Prince Tybalt? What is going on?

details.name: Prince Tybalt
details.text: I can explain everything, but not here. Please follow me to my camp. We can talk safely there.
